A whiteboard displays employers scheduling same-day interviews. Students exit with tote bags filled with business cards. Near the exit, a post-event survey link is flashed on the monitors, and camera crews from the university media team capture interviews, documenting the event and student interactions. Meanwhile, friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly to their efforts at the fair.

Alumni volunteers share quick pep talks near the coffee station, and a whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, contributing to the fair's focus on job readiness. Meanwhile, career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops, and some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall. Dozens of booths with colorful banners circle the polished floor. Additionally, workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom.
